snippet: Capt. Lucas Gruenther, whose F-16 fighter jet disappeared Monday during a training mission, was found Thursday in the Adriatic Sea, his family said.
abstract: Body of Capt Lucas Gruenther, United States Air Force pilot whose F-16 fighter jet disappeared during January 28 training mission, is found in Adriatic Sea.
lead_paragraph: Capt. Lucas Gruenther, whose F-16 fighter jet disappeared Monday during a training mission, was found Thursday in the Adriatic Sea, his family said.
